SUMMARY:Buffalo Bayou Park Wellness Walk
DTSTAMP:20260618T034736Z
DTSTART:20260708T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Buffalo Bayou Partnership on a free Wellness Walk led by L
	aura Conely\, founder of Urban Paths. Anyone and everyone is invited to wa
	lk through the paths of Buffalo Bayou Park while discussing topics includi
	ng mental and physical health as well as the benefits of being exposed to 
	nature. \nEn Español\nEl primer miércoles de cada mes\, la traductora Marc
	ella Cabrera se unirá al grupo para ofrecer la caminata guiada en español.
	 \nCost\nFree \nDuration\n90 minutes / 3 miles \nMeeting Location\nThe Wat
	er Works in Buffalo Bayou Park (105-B Sabine St) \nFREE REGISTRATION\n\nht
	tps://buffalobayou.org/event/2026-july-buffalo-bayou-park-wellness-walk-10
	6-2/\n\nFrom Buffalo Bayou Partnership
URL:https://buffalobayou.org/event/2026-july-buffalo-bayou-park-wellness-wa
	lk-106-2/
LOCATION:THE WATER WORKS\, 105 Sabine Street\, Houston\, TX\, 77007\, Unite
	d States
